comments: Stewart (DET) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Embiid (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) establishes a legal guarding position outside of the RA when the contact occurs from Jackson (DET) during his driving shot attempt.
Stewart (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Simmons (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) cleanly blocks Jackson (DET) during his driving shot attempt.
Stewart (DET) clamps Embiid's (PHI) arm after his gather and affects his driving shot attempt.
Stewart (DET) establishes a screening position outside of Green's (PHI) path while out of bounds.
Grant (DET) swipes down and makes contact to Simmons' (PHI) head during his driving shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) legally contests Grant's (DET) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Grant (DET) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Thybulle (PHI) makes contact with Wright's (DET) body that affects his SQBR.
Wright (DET) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Green (PHI) retreats his arms to a vertical position and any contact with Grant (DET) is marginal.
